                  "<p>The Wayward Hermetic Spiritspeaker will summon identical Radiant Reflections and hide amongst them. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">Destroy all the Radiant Reflections' Elemental Wards</span> during this time to reveal and weaken the real body. Additionally, Iktomisaurs and Masters of the Night-Wind characters can<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\"> Hold their Aim over Radiant Reflections</span> to pause their movement for a short time...</p>"
